==Korean==
===Verb===
'''있다''' (itta)
#To be (in a place)
#:뉴욕 시는 미국에 '''있다'''. New York City '''is''' in the United States. 
#There is/there are
#:물속에 물고기가 '''있어'''요. '''There''' are fish in the water. 
#To have
#:그녀에게 남자친구가 '''있어'''요. She '''has''' a boyfriend. 
#(auxiliary) indicates a resultant state or location
#:서 '''있다''' be standing
#:모여 '''있다''' be gathered 
#(auxiliary) indicates an action in progress
#:울고 '''있다'''. be crying

